data.eml:eml: A new genus of scutigerid centipedes (Chilopoda) from Western Australia, with new characters for morphological phylogenetics of Scutigeromorpha

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Edgecombe, Gregory D., Barrow, Lauren (2007): A new genus of scutigerid centipedes (Chilopoda) from Western Australia, with new characters for morphological phylogenetics of Scutigeromorpha. Zootaxa 1409: 23-50, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.175540
